00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:51.150
So, in operations,
in a craft thing,

00:04:51.150 --> 00:04:53.090
a person is working
on a single item.

00:04:53.090 --> 00:04:56.363
In mass production, the idea
is you make a lot of them,

00:04:56.363 --> 00:04:57.530
and you put them in a queue.

00:04:57.530 --> 00:04:59.900
You make more, and you
put them in a queue.

00:04:59.900 --> 00:05:01.940
