mastery of the craft.

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:14.830
In mass production,
it's reduced unit cost

00:05:14.830 --> 00:05:17.360
and increased efficiency.

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:19.820
In lean, it's
eliminating all waste

00:05:19.820 --> 00:05:22.777
and only doing
value-added activities.

00:05:22.777 --> 00:05:24.610
You're going to be
