00:06:41.260 --> 00:06:45.460
In the craft world, it was
the master-driven continuous

00:06:45.460 --> 00:06:46.600
improvement.

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:48.100
In the mass production
world, it was

00:06:48.100 --> 00:06:50.808
the expert-driven
periodic improvement.

00:06:50.808 --> 00:06:52.350
We'd bring in the
consulting company.

00:06:52.350 --> 00:06:54.150
They'd tell us how to improve.

00:06:54.150 --> 00:06:56.370
Here it's the worker
does the improvement

00:06:56.370 --> 00:06:58.440
in a continuous way.

00:06:58.440 --> 00:07:01.080
The worker is a
continuous problem solver.

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:02.970
So I spent a lot of
time on that chart

00:07:02.970 --> 00:07:06.310
because this really sets
