00:07:06.310 --> 00:07:09.550
And, when we wrote
a book on this,

00:07:09.550 --> 00:07:11.470
we struggled with
how we define lean.

00:07:11.470 --> 00:07:12.970
And here's the term
we came up with.

00:07:12.970 --> 00:07:17.260
Lean thinking is the
dynamic, knowledge-driven,

00:07:17.260 --> 00:07:19.810
customer-focused
process through which

00:07:19.810 --> 00:07:23.590
all people in an enterprise
continuously eliminate waste

00:07:23.590 --> 00:07:25.520
and create value.

