00:41:15.183 --> 00:41:16.600
where they reduced
the readmission

00:41:16.600 --> 00:41:20.140
rate for COPD patients.

00:41:20.140 --> 00:41:23.050
Children's Hospital in
Seattle reduced its capital

00:41:23.050 --> 00:41:26.410
expenditures by $180 million
